> Hi Greg,
> maybe it's just a matter of taste but I think that is better to do
> something like this:
> 
> static char *actions[] = {
>         [KOBJ_ADD]      = "add",
>         [KOBJ_REMOVE]   = "remove",
>         [KOBJ_CHANGE]   = "change",
>         [KOBJ_MOUNT]    = "mount",
> };
> 
> This would prevent the insertion of a new action in the wrong place.
